elements.name: Verify API: getProcessCount API return Total Process Count

steps.name: "System_Admin" User invoke "getProcessCount"
User calls "getProcessCount" API with "Get" http Request
Verify Process_Count result is greater than 0
The API call is success with StatusCode 200

elements.name: Verify API: createProcess API add Process paylod

steps.name: "System_Admin" User "Add" Process Payload with Param = "none"
User calls "createProcess" API with "Post" http Request
The API call is success with StatusCode 200
Verify response will return Process instance
"processUpdatedBy" in response body is "NA"
"processUpdatedAt" in response body is "0000-00-00 00:00:00"
processId in response body is equal to output of "getActivityCount"
processCode in response body is equal to output of "PRS_getProcessCount"
Verify Total Process_Count increased by 1

elements.name: Verify API: createProcess API with no process Body

steps.name: "System_Admin" User "Add" Process Payload  with no Process Body and Param = "none"
User calls "createProcess" API with "Post" http Request
The API call is success with StatusCode 400

"message" in response body is "Required request body is missing: public com.ibm.dc.process.entity.Process com.ibm.dc.process.controller.ProcessController.createProcess(java.lang.String,com.ibm.dc.process.entity.Process)"

arguments.val: "Required request body is missing: public com.ibm.dc.process.entity.Process com.ibm.dc.process.controller.ProcessController.createProcess(java.lang.String,com.ibm.dc.process.entity.Process)"

elements.name: Verify API: getAllProcess API return List of All Process

steps.name: "System_Admin" User invoke "getAllProcess"
User calls "getAllProcess" API with "Get" http Request
The API call is success with StatusCode 200
Verify response will return List of Process
Total number of Process in List is equal to getProcessCount
Created Process should exist in the List of Process
